            "title": "盤中速報 - 集中市場加權指數下跌-519.19點至25504.66點，跌幅2%",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間26日09:58，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>下跌519.19點（或2%），暫報25504.66點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+0.99%</li><li>近 1 月：+7.19%</li><li>近 3 月：+16.02%</li><li>近 6 月：+16.84%</li><li>今年以來：+12.97%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>車用記憶體概念領跌-4.48%。其中    南亞科(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2408:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2408\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2408-TW</a>)            下跌        7.83%            ;        宜鼎(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:5289:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/5289\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">5289-TW</a>)            下跌        5.66%            ;        華邦電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2344:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2344\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2344-TW</a>)            下跌        5.54%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>18吋晶圓概念領跌-4.22%。其中    盟立(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2464:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2464\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2464-TW</a>)            下跌        5.89%            ;        中砂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1560:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1560\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1560-TW</a>)            下跌        4.26%            ;        家登(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3680:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3680\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3680-TW</a>)            下跌        4.21%    。</p></section></main>",
